REFERENCE  (J,PR/C,113,024609,2026)
FACILITY   (VDGT,3BZLUSP) 8 MV Pelletron
SAMPLE     Two secondary targets: 197Au (3.9 mg/cm2) and
            27Al (2.9 mg/cm2).
INC-SOURCE 9Be(7Li,6He)10B produced the 6He beam using a 24 MeV
            7Li beam incident on an 8 um-thick 9Be target.
DETECTOR   (TELES,SI,SI) Four DE-E telescopes with 25-40 um and
            1000 um thickness, 150 mm2 area Si telescope and
            solid angles from 5.5 msr to 16.9 msr.
ANALYSIS   (NTRTH) Normalized to 6He+197Au Rutherford value
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical uncertainty
STATUS     (APRVD) Proof-read by K.C.C.Pires (2026-03-09)
